WEBVTT

00:06:59.316 --> 00:07:02.394
na zimepewa jina "'Isiyo na
jina'(Wapenzi Kamilifu)."

00:07:03.431 --> 00:07:05.543
Lakini mtazamo wa karibu unafanya utambue

00:07:05.567 --> 00:07:08.716
kwamba hizi ni saa mbili zitumiazo betri,

00:07:08.740 --> 00:07:10.575
ambapo inakufanya kuelewa --

00:07:10.599 --> 00:07:11.841
"Hebu, subiri kidogo ...

00:07:11.865 --> 00:07:14.568
Moja ya betri itasimama kabla ya nyenzake.

00:07:14.592 --> 00:07:17.748
Moja ya hizi saa itakuja kupunguza
mwendo na kufa kabla ya nyingine

00:07:17.772 --> 00:07:20.255
na itaenda kuongeza usawa
wa kazi hii ya sanaa."

00:07:21.073 --> 00:07:24.181
Vile tu unavyoliwaza hilo jambo

00:07:24.205 --> 00:07:27.497
hujumuisha uhitaji wa mpango wa dharura.

00:07:28.687 --> 00:07:31.367
Unahitaji kuwa na dharura kwa
yale yasiyoonekana,